sections.heading: for foreclosure or satisfaction; where filed
sections.text: All complaints for the foreclosure or satisfaction of mortgages shall be filed in the district court where the mortgaged premises are situated.SourceR.S.1867, Code § 845, p. 542;R.S.1913, § 8254;C.S.1922, § 9207;C.S.1929, § 20-2139;R.S.1943, § 25-2137;Law
